# Common Interview Mistakes

❌ JVM contains JDK.

✅ JDK contains JRE, and JRE contains JVM.

---

❌ Java compiler generates machine code.

✅ Java compiler generates bytecode.

---

❌ JRE is used to develop Java applications.

✅ JDK is used for development.

---

❌ Bytecode is machine language.

✅ Bytecode is an intermediate language executed by the JVM.

